ZH: 我今天穿了一套新的服装。
EN: I am wearing a new outfit today.

ZH: 她购买了很多时尚的服饰。
EN: She bought a lot of stylish clothing.

ZH: 这件外套很暖和。
EN: This coat is very warm.

ZH: 他喜欢穿运动服来锻炼身体。
EN: He likes to wear sports clothes to exercise.

ZH: 她总是穿戴得非常整齐。
EN: She always dresses very neatly.

ZH: 这条围巾和帽子很搭配。
EN: This scarf and hat match well.

ZH: 我需要一身得体的礼服。
EN: I need a formal dress.

ZH: 他穿着一件格子衬衫。
EN: He is wearing a checkered shirt.

ZH: 她喜欢穿高跟鞋。
EN: She likes to wear high heels.

ZH: 这双拖鞋很舒适。
EN: These slippers are very comfortable.

ZH: 她的秋冬服装总是很时尚。
EN: Her fall and winter outfits are always very fashionable.

ZH: 这件夹克太紧了。
EN: This jacket is too tight.

ZH: 我要去购买一些新的户外服装。
EN: I am going to buy some new outdoor clothing.

ZH: 这顶帽子很时尚。
EN: This hat is very stylish.

ZH: 他的衬衫搭配领带非常时髦。
EN: His shirt with a tie is very fashionable.

ZH: 这条裙子太短了。
EN: This skirt is too short.

